### Arabic

فَغَفَرْنَا لَهُۥ ذَٰلِكَ ۖ وَإِنَّ لَهُۥ عِندَنَا لَزُلْفَىٰ وَحُسْنَ مَـَٔابٍ

### English

So We forgave that for him. And he will indeed have ˹a status of˺ closeness to Us and an honourable destination!